snippet.title: Project Sakura Wars | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Project Sakura Wars is headed to the West for the PlayStation 4 in Spring 2020! The first mainline entry in over a decade, cherry blossoms will bloom once again next year.

Website: https://games.sega.com/sakurawars/
